  <LocalizationPair Name="%TechnologyDefinitionEconomyAndTrade26AutomatonsTitle">Superscale Uniform Standards</LocalizationPair>
  <LocalizationPair Name="%TechnologyDefinitionEconomyAndTrade26AutomatonsDescription">Automatons could be said to be a far more uniform and devout species than any other when it comes to manufacturing, and thus enforcing stricter regulations would have minimal effect. However there is always more to improve in the process of exchanging materials, storing industry and so on, especially if it is done aboard spaceships.</LocalizationPair>

