  <!-- System Improvements -->
  <!-- Fabrication License Replacement, adds +15% interest bonus and the base bonuses -->
  <LocalizationPair Name="%StarSystemImprovementIndustry6AutomatonsTitle">Industrial Refining Operation</LocalizationPair>
  <LocalizationPair Name="%StarSystemImprovementIndustry6AutomatonsDescription">An Automaton factory has to abide by many rules in order to emit as little polluants as possible, and has to have excess space in order to accomodate for the unique "stored industry" of the Automatons. This improvement helps refine the methods used in the factory and to refine the stored industry in a more compact form alongside to reuse it in order to accrue more interest on it.</LocalizationPair>

  <LocalizationPair Name="%StarSystemImprovementDenseOrbitalsTitle">Superstructural Orbitals</LocalizationPair>
  <LocalizationPair Name="%StarSystemImprovementDenseOrbitalsDescription">Once upon a time, the size of orbital platforms was limited by certain parameters, such as gravity, the size of the orbital and other factors. But the technologies learned from the other civilisations have allowed the Automatons to manufacture massive orbitals, allowing for greater productivity and population densitity than ever before.</LocalizationPair>

  <LocalizationPair Name="%TechnologyDefinitionUnique10AutomatonsTitle">Dense Orbitals</LocalizationPair>
  <LocalizationPair Name="%TechnologyDefinitionUnique10AutomatonsDescription">The Automatons may not be the most driven explorers, they are efficient when it comes to using new technologies. The Automatons have managed to create vast orbital platforms using the technology and techniques of encountered species.</LocalizationPair>

